<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440040' id='t-440040'>and the local golf course</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='441560' id='t-441560'>is being watered with water</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443440' id='t-443440'>that used to be
in a sewage treatment plant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446400' id='t-446400'>We've been doing this
for a couple of decades now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449360' id='t-449360'>But what we're learning
from our experience</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='451400' id='t-451400'>is that this approach is much more
