<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='562480' id='t-562480'>that in the summertime consists
almost entirely of wastewater effluent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566120' id='t-566120'>from cities like Riverside
and San Bernardino.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569160' id='t-569160'>The water comes
into our treatment wetland,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571240' id='t-571240'>it's exposed to sunlight and algae</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573600' id='t-573600'>and those break down
