<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617480' id='t-617480'>if it were their sole water supply.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620280' id='t-620280'>The third tap that we need to open up
