</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639760' id='t-639760'>In the current drought,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641240' id='t-641240'>we've seen that it's possible</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642840' id='t-642840'>to have our lawns survive
