</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='663760' id='t-663760'>The fourth and final water tap
that we need to open up</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666800' id='t-666800'>to solve our urban water problem</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668720' id='t-668720'>will flow with desalinated seawater.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671360' id='t-671360'>Now, I know what you probably heard
