<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694800' id='t-694800'>in the past two decades.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696920' id='t-696920'>This picture shows you</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698600' id='t-698600'>the largest seawater desalination plant
