<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713720' id='t-713720'>to produce a gallon of water.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715840' id='t-715840'>But just because seawater desalination
