</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='732560' id='t-732560'>So there it is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733800' id='t-733800'>With these four sources of water,</span>
